article_text:
UnitedHealth Group Inc. is scheduled to announce its first-quarter earnings before the market opens Tuesday. Here’s what you need to know:

EARNINGS FORECAST: Net income of $1.72 a share for the first quarter is the consensus of analysts surveyed by Thomson Reuters, compared with $1.46 reported a year earlier. UnitedHealth on Jan. 19 said its earnings projection for 2016 was between $7.60 and $7.80 a share.
